8. OWNER / BUILDER MODE

During development and testing, the app needs a simple owner/builder workflow.

This is not a public customer feature.

This is not a login system.

Do not build:
- authentication
- user roles
- admin dashboard
- password protection
- account management
- backend admin tools

For now, owner/builder mode simply means:

- preserve the editor view while testing
- do not automatically return to the landing page
- do not reload or reset the workspace unnecessarily
- do not clear settings unless Reset is clicked
- do not interrupt the owner’s testing workflow
- allow the owner to work for more than a few minutes without being sent back to the landing page

The editor should remain stable while testing.

